<section id="experience" class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Work Experience</h2>
        <div class="experience-grid">
            <div class="card experience-card">
                <div class="experience-header">
                    <h3>DevOps Engineer Intern</h3>
                    <p class="company">StarAgile Pvt. Ltd.</p>
                    <p class="duration">November 2024 - May 2025</p>
                </div>
                <ul class="achievements">
                    <li>Built optimized CI/CD pipelines with Jenkins, Docker, Git, SonarQube, and Nexus, and automated AWS infrastructure using Terraform, CloudFormation, and CodePipeline, achieving 60% faster deployments and 35% better code quality.</li>
                    <li>Deployed containerized microservices via Kubernetes, ECS, ECR, and Tomcat, cutting costs by 25% with autoscaling and resource limits.</li>
                    <li>Configured Ansible for consistent environment and app delivery across dev/staging, reducing onboarding time by 40%.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="card experience-card">
                <div class="experience-header">
                    <h3>Professor</h3>
                    <p class="company">Thakur College of Science and Commerce</p>
                    <p class="duration">August 2024 - May 2025</p>
                </div>
                <ul class="achievements">
                    <li>Over 1+ year of academic teaching experience, delivering core subjects like C++, Operating Systems, Networking, IoT, and Cloud Computing with practical implementation.</li>
                    <li>Led hands-on workshops on Python, Arduino, and emerging technologies, enhancing real-world skills and boosting student engagement by 30%.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="card experience-card">
                <div class="experience-header">
                    <h3>DevOps Intern</h3>
                    <p class="company">Cloud Counselage Pvt. Ltd.</p>
                    <p class="duration">Feb 2024 - May 2024</p>
                </div>
                <ul class="achievements">
                    <li>Spearheaded CI/CD pipeline development with Jenkins and Docker, reducing manual tasks by 80% and enhancing efficiency, with SonarQube and OWASP tools integrated for code quality and security.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--text);
    }

    .experience-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 2rem;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .experience-card {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .experience-header {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .experience-header h3 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--accent);
    }

    .company {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        margin: 0.25rem 0;
    }

    .duration {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--text);
        opacity: 0.8;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .achievements {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .achievements li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .achievements li:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .experience-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        }
    }
</style>
